OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has spoken to Donald
OL,8,FTrump about the need for a "practical
OL,9,Fplan" to get shipping going through
OL,10,Fthe Strait of Hormuz in the wake of
OL,11,Fthe Middle East ceasefire.
OL,13,FIt comes as the Prime Minister was
OL,14,Fvisiting allies in the Gulf for talks
OL,15,Fon how to support the pause in
OL,16,Ffighting and secure a permanent
OL,17,Freopening of the key shipping strait.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
