CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FHe is set to head back to the UK on
OL,8,FFriday after visiting Qatar, Bahrain,
OL,9,FSaudi Arabia and the United Arab
OL,10,FEmirates.
OL,12,FOn Thursday a Downing Street
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "The Prime Minister
OL,14,Fspoke to President Trump from Qatar
OL,15,Fthis evening.
OL,26,@uD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
