OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,F"The Prime Minister set out his
OL,8,Fdiscussions with Gulf leaders and
OL,9,Fmilitary planners in the region on the
OL,10,Fneed to restore freedom of navigation
OL,11,Fin the Strait of Hormuz, as well as
OL,12,Fthe UK's efforts to convene partners
OL,13,Fto agree a viable plan.
OL,15,F"They agreed that now there is a
OL,16,Fceasefire in place and agreement to
OL,17,Fopen the strait, we are at the next
OL,18,Fstage of finding a resolution.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,F"The leaders discussed the need for a
OL,8,Fpractical plan to get shipping moving
OL,9,Fagain as quickly as possible."
OL,11,FSir Keir earlier said the ships
OL,12,Fpassing through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,13,Fmust have "toll-free navigation" as
OL,14,Fpart of the ceasefire amid reports
OL,15,FIran wants to charge for passage.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@^O]uD@KOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FAsked whether he viewed the critical
OL,8,Fstrait as now being open, he said:
OL,9,F"There are a lot of things being said
OL,10,F` they need to be tested" and that the
OL,11,FUK's position is that "open" means
OL,12,F"open for safe navigation".
OL,14,F"That means toll-free navigation and
OL,15,Fvessels can get through," he told
OL,16,FITV's Talking Politics Podcast.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@YO]sD@WOUsD@\O]tD@AOUtD@ZO]vD@
OL,26,AAOUwD@YO]
