OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FSpeaking in London, the Foreign
OL,8,FSecretary also called for toll-free
OL,9,Ftravel through the Strait, warning
OL,10,Fthat trading routes from Qatar, UAE,
OL,11,FBahrain, Kuwait, Iraq, Saudi Arabia
OL,12,Fand Oman were "all hijacked by Iran so
OL,13,Fthat they can hold the global economy
OL,14,Fhostage".
OL,16,FYvette Cooper said: "The fundamental
OL,17,Ffreedoms of the seas must not be
OL,18,Funilaterally withdrawn or sold off to
OL,19,Findividual bidders and nor can there
OL,20,Fbe any place for tolls on an
OL,21,Finternational waterway."
OL,26,@tD@OOUvD@HO]xD@UOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
