OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FThe US president later posted on his
OL,8,FTruth Social platform: "There are
OL,9,Freports that Iran is charging fees to
OL,10,Ftankers going through the Hormuz
OL,11,FStrait ` They better not be and, if
OL,12,Fthey are, they better stop now!
OL,13,FPresident DONALD J. TRUMP."
OL,15,FHe added in a separate post: "Iran is
OL,16,Fdoing a very poor job, dishonorable
OL,17,Fsome would say, of allowing Oil to go
OL,18,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz. That is
OL,19,Fnot the agreement we have!"
OL,26,@pD@XOUuD@[O]wD@^OU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
