OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FMr Trump agreed a two-week truce
OL,8,Fearlier this week with the reopening
OL,9,Fof the strait a key condition.
OL,11,FBut the agreement soon came under
OL,12,Fstrain as Israel's bombardment of
OL,13,FBeirut prompted Iran to close the
OL,14,Fshipping lane again amid disagreement
OL,15,Fover whether Lebanon was included in
OL,16,Fthe ceasefire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
