CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FHowever, Israeli Prime Minister
OL,8,FBenjamin Netanyahu said on Thursday he
OL,9,Fhad authorised direct talks with
OL,10,FLebanon "as soon as possible" aimed at
OL,11,Fdisarming Iranian-backed Hezbollah
OL,12,Fmilitants and establishing relations
OL,13,Fbetween the neighbours.
OL,15,FSir Keir said Israeli strikes on
OL,16,FLebanon are "wrong" and that it should
OL,17,Fbe included in the ceasefire.
OL,26,@rD@IOUrD@]O]xD@MOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
