OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FHis call with Mr Trump also came hours
OL,8,Fafter he was asked about the US
OL,9,Fpresident's language in his posts
OL,10,Fabout Iran and said they were "not
OL,11,Fwords I would use".
OL,13,F"Let me be really clear and blunt
OL,14,Fabout this ` they're not words I would
OL,15,Fuse or would ever use because I come
OL,16,Fat this with our British values and
OL,17,Fprinciples foremost and uppermost in
OL,18,Fmy mind," he said.
OL,26,@rD@_OUsD@RO]uD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
