OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FThe US leader has repeatedly lashed
OL,8,Fout publicly at Sir Keir in recent
OL,9,Fweeks over his failure to initially
OL,10,Fallow Washington to use UK bases.
OL,12,FHe reiterated on Thursday that the US
OL,13,Fis only authorised to use UK bases for
OL,14,F"collective self-defence" and said the
OL,15,FUK is "monitoring" to make sure that
OL,16,Fis the case.
OL,18,FElsewhere, Sir Keir wrote in The
OL,19,FGuardian newspaper that "Iran must now
OL,20,Fbecome a line in the sand".
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@YO]wD@GOUwD@RO]{D@YOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
