OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775782987
OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FHe said: "How we emerge from this
OL,8,Fcrisis will define all of us for a
OL,9,Fgeneration.
OL,11,F"And, instead of hoping to return to
OL,12,Fthe world of 2008, we will forge a new
OL,13,Fpath for Britain ` one that
OL,14,Fstrengthens our energy, our defence
OL,15,Fand our economic security in a new
OL,16,Fage."
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@AOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
