OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FA Downing Street spokesperson said
OL,8,Fthat during his Middle East tour, Sir
OL,9,FKeir discussed "the need to push to
OL,10,Frestore the free flow of goods to
OL,11,Fsupport global supply chains" with
OL,12,FUnited Arab Emirates (UAE) President
OL,13,FSheikh Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan.
OL,15,FThe Prime Minister also "expressed
OL,16,Fsolidarity with the people of the UAE
OL,17,Fand his condolences for the lives lost
OL,18,Fas a result of Iran's reckless
OL,19,Fbombardment", according to No 10.
OL,26,@qD@POUsD@]O]wD@YOU{D@LO]
