OL,3,CPM and Trump discuss need for
OL,4,C'practical plan' to reopen strait amid
OL,5,CGulf visit
OL,7,FIn talks with leaders from Bahrain,
OL,8,FSir Keir "reiterated the importance of
OL,9,Fensuring the ceasefire is upheld in
OL,10,Forder to pave the way for lasting
OL,11,Fpeace".
OL,26,@pD@JOUsD@FO]
